This routine is called for every recipient address.
It can return
.b TRUE
to indicate that the address is acceptable
and mail processing will continue,
or it can return
.b FALSE
to reject the recipient.
If it returns false,
it is up to
.i checkcompat
to print an error message
(using
.i usrerr )
